create procedure [dbo].[temp_insupd_test] @t_test_id uniqueidentifier  
as
 
	UPDATE [dbo].[T_TEST]
	   SET [OBJ_NAME] = t2.OBJ_NAME,
		  [TIMELIMITMIN] = t2.TIMELIMITMIN,
		  [ORDER_NUM] = t2.ORDER_NUM,
		  [ACTUAL_MARK] = t2.ACTUAL_MARK,
		  [T_TEST_ID] = t2.T_TEST_ID,
		  [NOTES_LANG1] = t2.NOTES_LANG1,
		  [PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG1] = t2.PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG1,
		  [PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG2] = t2.PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG2,
		  [PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG3] = t2.PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG3,
		  [NOTES_LANG2] = t2.NOTES_LANG2, 
		  [NOTES_LANG3] = t2.NOTES_LANG3, 
		  [BACK_BTN_MARK] = t2.BACK_BTN_MARK,
		  [USER_QUESTION_MARK] = t2.USER_QUESTION_MARK,
		  [BACK_ONLY_1_STEP] = t2.BACK_ONLY_1_STEP,
		  [STOP_TIMES] = t2.STOP_TIMES, 
		  [SHOW_QUESTION_MARK] = t2.SHOW_QUESTION_MARK
	from T_TEST t1
	inner join tmp_t_test t2 on t1.t_test_id = t2.t_test_id
	WHERE t2.t_test_id = @t_test_id

[t2].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG1],[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG2] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG2] as [t2].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG2],[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG3] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG3] as [t2].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG3],[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST].[NOTES_LANG2] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST].[NOTES_LANG2] as [t2].[NOTES_LANG2],[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST].[NOTES_LANG3] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST].[NOTES_LANG3] as [t2].[NOTES_LANG3],[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST].[BACK_BTN_MARK] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST].[BACK_BTN_MARK] as [t2].[BACK_BTN_MARK],[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST].[USER_QUESTION_MARK] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST].[USER_QUESTION_MARK] as [t2].[USER_QUESTION_MARK],[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST].[BACK_ONLY_1_STEP] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST].[BACK_ONLY_1_STEP] as [t2].[BACK_ONLY_1_STEP],[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST].[STOP_TIMES] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST].[STOP_TIMES] as [t2].[STOP_TIMES],[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST].[SHOW_QUESTION_MARK] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST].[SHOW_QUESTION_MARK] as [t2].[SHOW_QUESTION_MARK]
CASE WHEN [Expr1004] AND [Expr1008] THEN (0) ELSE (1) END
CASE WHEN [Expr1006] AND [Expr1008] THEN (0) ELSE (1) END
CASE WHEN [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST].[OBJ_NAME] as [t1].[OBJ_NAME] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST].[OBJ_NAME] as [t2].[OBJ_NAME] THEN (1) ELSE (0) END
CASE WHEN [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST].[ORDER_NUM] as [t1].[ORDER_NUM] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST].[ORDER_NUM] as [t2].[ORDER_NUM] THEN (1) ELSE (0) END
CASE WHEN [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST].[T_TEST_ID] as [t1].[T_TEST_ID] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST].[T_TEST_ID] as [t2].[T_TEST_ID] THEN (1) ELSE (0) END

CASE WHEN NOT [Pass1056] AND NOT [Expr1055] IS NULL THEN (0) ELSE CASE WHEN NOT [Pass1058] AND NOT [Expr1057] IS NULL THEN (1) ELSE CASE WHEN NOT [Pass1060] AND NOT [Expr1059] IS NULL THEN (2) ELSE CASE WHEN NOT [Pass1062] AND NOT [Expr1061] IS NULL THEN (3) ELSE NULL END END END END

INSERT INTO [dbo].[T_TEST]
           ([OBJ_NAME]
           ,[OBJ_CREATED]
           ,[OBJ_CREATED_BY]
           ,[TIMELIMITMIN]
           ,[ORDER_NUM]
           ,[ACTUAL_MARK]
           ,[T_TEST_ID]
           ,[NOTES_LANG1]
           ,[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG1]
           ,[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG2]
           ,[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG3]
           ,[NOTES_LANG2]
           ,[NOTES_LANG3]
           ,[BACK_BTN_MARK]
           ,[USER_QUESTION_MARK]
           ,[BACK_ONLY_1_STEP]
           ,[STOP_TIMES]
           ,[SHOW_QUESTION_MARK])
select     
           t2.OBJ_NAME,
           getdate(),
           t2.OBJ_CREATED_BY,
           t2.TIMELIMITMIN,
           t2.ORDER_NUM,
           t2.ACTUAL_MARK,
           t2.T_TEST_ID,
           t2.NOTES_LANG1,
           t2.PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG1,
           t2.PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG2,
           t2.PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG3,
           t2.NOTES_LANG2,
           t2.NOTES_LANG3,
           t2.BACK_BTN_MARK,
           t2.USER_QUESTION_MARK,
           t2.BACK_ONLY_1_STEP,
           t2.STOP_TIMES,
           t2.SHOW_QUESTION_MARK
	from 
	tmp_t_test t2 
	WHERE t2.t_test_id = @t_test_id
    and t2.t_test_id not in (select t1.t_test_id from T_TEST t1)
